-- MOVES-Investec Asset Management hires Mike Hugman from Amiya Capital
-- By Anet Josline Pinto in Bangalore
-- Tue Oct 14, 2014 10:05AM EDT
-- None



Oct 14 (Reuters) - Investec Asset Management, a subsidiary of Investec Group, said it appointed Mike Hugman as a strategist in its global emerging markets fixed income team.

Hugman will focus on further developing proprietary and innovative research within the 28-member team, Investec said in a statement.